OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 16 Jul to Sat 25 JulFA
OL,6,Fchange in weather pattern is likely at
OL,7,Fthe start of this period, with the
OL,8,Fpreceding dry and sunny weather
OL,9,Fbreaking down into a more unsettled
OL,10,Fspell. This means an increasing chance
OL,11,Fof showers by Thursday and into the
OL,12,Ffollowing weekend. Some heavy and
OL,13,Fthundery showers are likely,
OL,14,Fparticularly across the south of the
OL,15,FUK. Into the following week,
OL,16,Fconditions will likely remain
OL,17,Fchangeable with showers or longer
OL,18,Fspells of rain at times, perhaps heavy
OL,19,Fand thundery in places. Temperatures
OL,20,Fare likely to be above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
