OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 26 Jul to Sun 9 Aug
OL,6,FChangeable weather patterns are
OL,7,Fexpected during this period. Showers
OL,8,For some longer spells of rain are
OL,9,Flikely at times, perhaps heavy and
OL,10,Fthundery. Some drier and brighter
OL,11,Finterludes are also possible,
OL,12,Fespecially in the south and southeast.
OL,13,FTemperatures are likely to be above
OL,14,Fnormal with some hot spells possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
